                            <decoNote>
                                <ab>Red painted linear frame, whose top and bottom lines are in the form of palm
                                    branches. The side lines are decorated with a palm branch motif internally and a dotted
                                    zig-zag pattern externally.</ab>
                                <locus>Around the inscription</locus>
                            </decoNote>
                            <decoNote>
                                <ab>Seven-branched candelabrum flanked on its left by an Ark of the
                                    Covenant, and on its right by a ram's horn and a lulav. The
                                    candelabrum and Ark of the Covenant are embellished with a palm
                                    branch like motif</ab>
